C. MANDATORY STEPS FOR LLD DESIGN

1. Clarify requirements

=> Functional: Insert card, validate PIN, check balance, withdraw, deposit, change PIN.
=> Non-Functional: Secure PIN handling, proper state management, transaction atomicity.
=> Assumptions: Single ATM, mocked bank server, simple cash dispensing.
=> Edge Cases: Wrong PIN, insufficient balance, card blocked, ATM cash low.

2. Identify entities and relationships

=> Main entities: ATM, Card, Account, Transaction, ATMState
=> Key relationships :
ATM has current state and current card.
Card belongs to one Account.
Transaction records every operation.

